(self.webpackChunklnnapi=self.webpackChunklnnapi||[]).push([[183],{7019:(e,c,a)=>{"use strict";a.r(c),a.d(c,{data:()=>d});const d={key:"v-01534233",path:"/zh-cn/http/sign.html",title:"签名",lang:"en-US",frontmatter:{},excerpt:"",headers:[],filePathRelative:"zh-cn/http/sign.md",git:{updatedTime:1625035966e3,contributors:[{name:"Lawetis-Lee",email:"es6china@163.com",commits:2},{name:"397702186@qq.com",email:"397702186@qq.com",commits:1}]}}},9303:(e,c,a)=>{"use strict";a.r(c),a.d(c,{default:()=>o});const d=(0,a(6252).uE)('<h1 id="签名" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#签名" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 签名</h1><p><code>POST</code>请求参数以<code>form</code>表单格式提交，<code>GET</code>请求以URL<code>query</code>参数提交，请求的所有参数须按照参数名进行<code>ASCII</code>值进行升序排序，然后使用<code>Ed25519</code>算法进行签名</p><p>例如对以下请求进行签名（模拟接口，仅作为签名示例使用）:</p><p>请求原始数据</p><div class="language-text ext-text"><pre class="shiki" style="background-color:#FFFFFF;"><code><span class="line"><span style="color:#000000;">http://127.0.0.1/api/user/CreateUser?UserId=3e4c12bd3a5a49174c7441271\n\nform表单参数:\nUnixTime=1582083351&amp;SecretId=5e4cabd3a5a49174c7421274\n</span></span></code></pre></div><p>密钥对信息</p><ul><li>私钥: <code>7a51d876f017c69479ae64f90e9e9b25d9130d7659c5694072d790b8166e4ab5</code></li><li>公钥: <code>bc9c5390c82c8e106086e9fa1d85b509821b9a27a83f7cb6d53872cd6020a601</code></li></ul><p>生成签名具体步骤如下:</p><ol><li>对参数按照参数名进行升序排序，排序后的内容如下</li></ol><div class="language-text ext-text"><pre class="shiki" style="background-color:#FFFFFF;"><code><span class="line"><span style="color:#000000;">SecretId=5e4cabd3a5a49174c7421274&amp;UnixTime=1582083351&amp;UserId=3e4c12bd3a5a49174c7441271\n</span></span></code></pre></div><ol start="2"><li>对以上排序后的请求字符串进行签名,签名结果为:</li></ol><div class="language-text ext-text"><pre class="shiki" style="background-color:#FFFFFF;"><code><span class="line"><span style="color:#000000;">2c85d50cdfada748cc251632aec3d64c14e49006a662cdcc1e8709212654f102f7ec22f2ebfa7cd709fe8ac65806ee78407ffc5e1c035ca672b3fac4155dbf04\n</span></span></code></pre></div><ol start="3"><li>将签名结果添加到请求末尾,参数名为<code>Sign</code>.最终请求的<code>form</code>表单参数为:</li></ol><div class="language-text ext-text"><pre class="shiki" style="background-color:#FFFFFF;"><code><span class="line"><span style="color:#000000;">SecretId=5e4cabd3a5a49174c7421274&amp;UnixTime=1582083351&amp;Sign=d14f046ccd7048fed140d418393053e61caff53f839724153589daa365218f9929312db0eba3edb947fbbaff6697a427ce094dc2ac576b9d5583429bb5fe7606\n</span></span></code></pre></div><ul><li><code>HTTP</code>请求对<code>query</code>参数和<code>form</code>表单参数都会进行签名</li><li>参数中的<code>Sign</code>不参与签名, 根据<code>HTTP</code>规则，<code>GET</code>请求放在<code>query</code>参数末尾，<code>POST</code>请求放在<code>form</code>表单末尾</li><li><code>WebSocket</code>连接时需要把所有请求参数放置在<code>URL</code>中</li><li>请求的<code>URL</code>区分大小写，请确保和文档中的一致</li></ul>',15),o={render:function(e,c){return d}}}}]);